      <scopecontent id="aspace_70e460bdbbad31855ecc922a7cb3574b">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>The collection includes fliers, pamphlets, postcards, and objects produced by a variety of organizations working to make abortion illegal in the United States. Items were collected by Megann Licskai, most were distributed at "Vita et Veritas" conferences held on the Yale University campus in 2017 and 2018. Objects include fetus dolls, a pin, and a rubber bracelet.</p>
      </scopecontent>
